{"ts":"2026-07-10T16:20:02.384Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"## Problem\n`pm comments <id> --body \"...\"` fails with `Unknown option --body`. gh/glab muscle memory makes --body the reflexive flag for comment text; every fresh agent session pays ~2 wasted tool calls + a few hundred tokens rediscovering --add. Observed in a real session 2026-07-10 (vanilla @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.10).\n\n## Proposed fix\n1. Accept `--body <text>` as a hidden alias for `--add <text>` on `pm comments` (and mirror for `--edit` replacement text if cheap).\n2. Extend the unknown-option error path to suggest the nearest valid flag — the unknown-COMMAND suggester exists; unknown-OPTION suggestions are the gap (ranking defect on the command side is pm-g543 / GH-490, related edge).\n\n## Scope guard\nAlias only — no behavior change to --add; help output must not grow (hidden alias) per token-efficiency goals.\n\n## Source\nhttps://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/498"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-z32q"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-498: pm comments rejects --body — accept it as an alias for --add and hint on unknown options"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Upstream GH-498 (filed 2026-07-10). Agents trained on gh/glab reach for 'pm comments <id> --body ...' and hit 'Unknown option --body', costing a failed call plus a --help round-trip per fresh session on one of the highest-frequency write paths."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","cli","gh-issue","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-10T16:20:02.384Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-10T16:20:02.384Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":45},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm comments <id> --body <text> behaves exactly like --add <text> (hidden alias, help stays lean); unknown-option errors on comments suggest the nearest valid flag (e.g. --body -> --add); contract/completion/docs sites updated per the new-flag wiring checklist; regression test covers alias and suggestion; GH-498 closed with a comment linking the fix"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-g543","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-10T16:20:02.384Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"0f7ddd4a3519a916bec643ca7c6b02d254b212409a6e8dd5c0560fae6f052144","message":"Track GH-498 from ecosystem dogfooding"}
